      <h2 class="tldr__heading">How TechBrot pricing works.</h2>
      <p class="tldr__body" id="kitchen-sink-f2-pricing-tldr-body">Every TechBrot engagement is fixed-fee with a written scope agreed before any work begins &mdash; no hourly billing. Real ranges: <strong>monthly bookkeeping $400&ndash;$2,500+/month</strong>, cleanup $1,500&ndash;$15,000+, catch-up $2,000&ndash;$20,000+, QuickBooks setup $750&ndash;$5,000+, migration $2,500&ndash;$10,000+, payroll $150&ndash;$800+/month, sales tax compliance $250&ndash;$1,500+/month, and fractional CFO $3,000&ndash;$8,000+/month (by application). Where you land depends on real factors &mdash; transaction volume, number of accounts and entities, history depth, file complexity. The 30-minute discovery call is free; your exact fixed fee is delivered in writing within 3 business days. No long-term lock-in on recurring engagements. Tax filing isn&rsquo;t included (your CPA handles that), but a year-end CPA handoff is included free.</p>
